"{\"uid\": \"nbnnews.com.au-2024-05-08-central-coast-surfer-molly-picklum-selected-to-represent-australia-at-the-olympics\", \"text\": \"Adopted Novocastrian Tyler Wright and the Central Coast's Molly Picklum are among four surfers picked to represent Australia at the Olympics.  The team will go for gold at a fearsome break\\u2026 a world away from the French capital.\"}"